  "Description": {
    "English": "A thin, <span class=\"name name-stellar\">shimmering thread</span>, once owned by Iteration: Gemini. This impossible fibre, once a treasured keepsake, sings on the wavelength of the Space Anomaly.<br><br>A valuable and exotic component, this would be of great use to Iteration: Tethys in <span class=\"name name-technology\">repairing</span> the shattered Drone.",
    "SimplifiedChinese": "一根轻薄如蝉翼的<span class=\"name name-stellar\">发光丝线</span>，曾经属于迭代：双子。这种不可思议的纤维是上一任主人珍藏的纪念品，时刻咏唱着太空异象的波段。<br><br>极其珍贵的异星构件，能够帮助迭代：特提斯<span class=\"name name-technology\">修复</span>破碎的无人机。",
    "TraditionalChinese": "一條輕薄、<span class=\"name name-stellar\">閃閃發光的線</span>，曾經屬於迭代：傑米奈。這種不可思議的纖維曾經是珍貴的紀念品，在太空異常的波長中受到歌頌。<br><br>一種珍貴的奇特元件，在迭代：忒堤斯<span class=\"name name-technology\">修理</span>破碎的無人機時，會十分有用。"
  },
